    {
      "id": "9adffdf1_15e246d5",
      "file_path": "hv-collector-xnf-simulator/src/main/kotlin/org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/simulators/xnf/impl/adapters/XnfApiServer.kt",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 82,
      "message": "We should log also that we received request and for what id (as in current \"Sim info: $response\" log there is only info like \"not found\" or \"ongoing\" which is pretty useless in logs without context).\n\nSo we probably should do something like\n```\nlogger.info { \"Checking task status\" }\nval id = UUID.fromString(ctx.pathTokens[\"id\"])\nlogger.info { \"Checking status for id: $id\" }\nval status = ongoingSimulations.status(id)\nval response = Responses.statusResponse(status.toString(), status.message)\nlogger.info { \"Task $id status: $response\" }\nctx.response.sendAndHandleErrors(IO.just(response))",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3701,
        "name": "Filip Krzywka",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "filip.krzywka@nokia.com",
        "username": "fkrzywka"
      },
      "updated": "2018-12-03 13:12:18.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
